title: People who CAN'T be vegan: the ethics of doing the best you can.
description: Some people have serious health problems that make it impossible to be vegan —or, at least, make it extremely difficult to cope with conflict advice from doctors, and the way their own symptoms react to the foods vegans rely upon.  What about them?  In this video we hear a lot about Crohn's disease (from someone who didn't believe Durianrider's claims to have cured it with a vegan diet)  and, ultimately, about the ethics of just doing the best you can.
